# =============================================================================
# GitLab Runner Configuration
# =============================================================================

# Resource limits
GITLAB_RUNNER_CPU_LIMIT=2
GITLAB_RUNNER_MEMORY_LIMIT=4G

# =============================================================================
# Registration (use 'docker compose run --rm gitlab-runner register')
# =============================================================================
# The runner is registered interactively, not via environment variables.
# See README.md for registration instructions.
#
# You'll need:
# - GitLab instance URL (https://gitlab.com or self-hosted)
# - Registration token from: Project → Settings → CI/CD → Runners
# - Runner description/name
# - Tags (e.g., docker, self-hosted, production)
# - Executor type (docker recommended)
# =============================================================================
